1)==========Installation instructions============

You will need Geant4 and Root installed before compiling

to compile:

    configure
    make

to run:

    bdsimrun [options]

to run without Geant4 interactive propmt:

    bdsimrun -s 

to run in batch mode using PBS batch system:

    bdsimrun -b

Quit Geant4 session with  'exit' to save the Root file

2)==========Other files========================

xxx.optics           : sample optics file
BDSInput.cards   : sample cards file 
BDS_vis.mac      : sample G4 visualization script

